{
  "info": {
    "name": "Krypton E-commerce — Catálogo",
    "description": "Catálogo de productos y categorías de Krypton.\n\nFlujo sugerido:\n1. Corré 'Login (admin)' una vez → guarda el JWT en {{token}} (lo usan los endpoints /api/admin/**).\n2. La lectura del catálogo (GET /api/products, /api/categories) es PÚBLICA: no necesita token.\n3. 'Create category' y 'Create product' guardan el id devuelto en {{categoryId}} / {{productId}} para encadenar update/delete.\n\nBase URL por defecto: http://localhost:8080\nAdmin sembrado: admin@krypton.pe / Admin123!\n\nNotas de comportamiento:\n- GET público solo devuelve productos active=true; un producto soft-deleted no aparece y su GET /{id} da 404.\n- DELETE de producto es baja lógica (active=false), responde 204.\n- DELETE de categoría con productos asociados (incluidos soft-deleted) responde 409.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "adminEmail", "value": "admin@krypton.pe" },
    { "key": "adminPassword", "value": "Admin123!" },
    { "key": "categoryId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "productId", "value": "1" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth (obtener token ADMIN)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (admin) → guarda token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.token);",
                  "  console.log('Token ADMIN guardado en {{token}}');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{adminEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Login del admin sembrado (V3). El test script guarda el JWT en {{token}} para los endpoints /api/admin/**."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Catálogo (público — sin token)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List products",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/products", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "products"] },
            "description": "Listado público paginado. Solo productos active=true. No requiere token. Devuelve PageResponse: { content, page, size, totalElements, totalPages }."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Search products (filtros + paginación)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/products?name=&categoryId=&priceMin=&priceMax=&page=0&size=20&sort=name,asc",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "products"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "name", "value": "", "description": "substring del nombre (LIKE)", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "categoryId", "value": "", "description": "id de categoría", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "priceMin", "value": "", "description": "precio mínimo", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "priceMax", "value": "", "description": "precio máximo", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "page", "value": "0" },
                { "key": "size", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "sort", "value": "name,asc", "description": "campo,dir (Pageable)" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Misma ruta con filtros opcionales (JPA Specifications). Habilitá los query params que quieras combinar. Todos son opcionales; se componen entre sí."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get product by id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/products/{{productId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "products", "{{productId}}"] },
            "description": "Producto activo por id. 404 si no existe o está inactivo (soft-deleted)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List categories",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/categories", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "categories"] },
            "description": "Listado público de categorías. No requiere token."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get category by id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/categories/{{categoryId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "categories", "{{categoryId}}"] },
            "description": "Categoría por id. 404 si no existe."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Admin — Categorías (requiere token ADMIN)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create category → guarda categoryId",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('categoryId', res.id);",
                  "  console.log('categoryId =', res.id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/categories", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "admin", "categories"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Laptops\",\n  \"description\": \"Notebooks y ultrabooks\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Crea una categoría. name único (≤80), description opcional (≤255). 201 OK, 409 si el nombre ya existe, 403 con CLIENTE, 401 sin token."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update category",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/categories/{{categoryId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "admin", "categories", "{{categoryId}}"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Laptops Gamer\",\n  \"description\": \"Notebooks de alto rendimiento\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Actualiza la categoría {{categoryId}}. La unicidad de nombre excluye su propio id. 404 si no existe, 409 si el nombre choca con otra."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete category",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/categories/{{categoryId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "admin", "categories", "{{categoryId}}"] },
            "description": "Borra la categoría {{categoryId}}. 204 si está vacía. 409 si tiene productos asociados (incluidos soft-deleted) — guard referencial."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Admin — Productos (requiere token ADMIN)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create product → guarda productId",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('productId', res.id);",
                  "  console.log('productId =', res.id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/products", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "admin", "products"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"sku\": \"LAP-001\",\n  \"name\": \"Notebook Krypton 14\",\n  \"description\": \"Core i5, 16GB RAM, 512GB SSD\",\n  \"price\": 2999.90,\n  \"stock\": 25,\n  \"imageUrl\": \"https://example.com/lap-001.jpg\",\n  \"categoryId\": {{categoryId}}\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Crea un producto. sku único (≤60), price ≥0 (12,2), stock ≥0 (bootstrap inicial), categoryId debe existir. 201 OK, 409 si el sku existe, 400 si falta un campo requerido o la categoría no existe (404)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update product (stock se ignora)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/products/{{productId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "admin", "products", "{{productId}}"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"sku\": \"LAP-001\",\n  \"name\": \"Notebook Krypton 14 (2026)\",\n  \"description\": \"Core i7, 16GB RAM, 1TB SSD\",\n  \"price\": 3199.90,\n  \"stock\": 999,\n  \"imageUrl\": \"https://example.com/lap-001.jpg\",\n  \"categoryId\": {{categoryId}}\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Actualiza el producto {{productId}}. OJO: el campo stock es READ-ONLY en catálogo — se ignora silenciosamente (lo manejará inventario/checkout). sku único excluyendo su propio id."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete product (baja lógica)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/products/{{productId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "admin", "products", "{{productId}}"] },
            "description": "Soft-delete del producto {{productId}} (active=false). Responde 204. Tras esto desaparece de la lectura pública y su GET /{id} da 404, pero la fila persiste."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
